      <title>Beacon Roofing 敦促股东拒绝 QXO 的敌意收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/beacon-roofing-urges-shareholders-to-reject-hostile-qxo-bid</link>
